{"tid":840940,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如何做到二十下引體上升 － (三個常見誤區 & 解決方法)","createTime":"2018-09-29T07:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T17:29:46.000Z","uid":54636,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0d268c8f8a646ca7e8108182c4a2c437fa5a20d8","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sDiJmPImQt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsDiJmPImQt0&d=q6AjDh8bRvErRVkXioxescVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=82360be4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sDiJmPImQt0</a><br />\n<br />\n經驗分享，大家有乜問題都歡迎係提問<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw關於點樣做到引體上升，可以參考下上個post<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/742087/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/742087/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c32034d03598b0e793b96ab547fb6ff0c8fc2551","tid":840940,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"岩開始最少要幾下?"},{"pid":"f21ff7b5243c043598a0aaf77c1474c1a8caf1af","tid":840940,"uid":186799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:55:00.000Z","msg":"岩岩開始拉 最少要幾多下？"},{"pid":"3d5fb57674ae2a6bffa302560418f7d55bd8081a","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c32034d03598b0e793b96ab547fb6ff0c8fc2551","tid":840940,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"岩開始最少要幾下?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"唔係好明，最少要幾多下既意思係? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bceeffd7a25b2ad65e69cb8b6d63ba4e146944aa","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21ff7b5243c043598a0aaf77c1474c1a8caf1af","tid":840940,"uid":186799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-