88a","tid":840940,"uid":141164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c14c4edf12b55bdeee0638ceec751480d3073c40","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"41210d0dd4f65e38635d10ba43e060e85a094606","tid":840940,"uid":141164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"第一組拉到10下，之後第二組就得番6下，之後就4下，兩下，一下咁，應該點練"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:23:28.000Z","msg":"呢d情況一般都係建議留力，唔好組組拉到力歇 <br />\n<br />\n比如你maximum pull up 係10下<br />\n<br />\n就可以每組拉～6下左右，拉番7~8組 (最後一兩組先盡做) <br />\n<br />\n抖既時間可以長少少 around 3分鐘都冇問題，要防止乳酸積聚<br />\n<br />\n咁既做法，volume夠大，對reps / muscle building效果會好好多<br />\n<br />\n當然，咁既練法毋容置疑需時係比較長<br />\n<br />\n巴打要自己取捨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"好多謝巴打意見，下次試下先，會專登去練就唔會嫌時間長啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5c5a41322fbc1a28e4bce5779f280725a6033b","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"32138417afff2fa2781c4bd0e96b55da00897433","tid":840940,"uid":205996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d5fb57674ae2a6bffa302560418f7d55bd8081a","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c32034d03598b0e793b96ab547fb6ff0c8fc2551","tid":840940,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"岩開始最少要幾下?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"唔係好明，最少要幾多下既意思係? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:07:05.000Z","msg":"新手要練幾多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋點樣發力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"好睇巴打原本身體條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果原本就有能力拉到引體上升，可以直接練<br />\n<br />\n每組用 7~8成力，組間拉抖番2~3分鐘，新手黎講做番～5組已經好夠 （&lt;包保第日肌肉會痛)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲未拉到既朋友，可以先練斜拉/離心收縮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GZdTVibD2Nc&amp;t=219s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGZdTVibD2Nc%26t%3D219s&d=q6AjDh8bRvErRVkXioxescVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b1affe10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GZdTVibD2Nc&amp;t=219s</a><br />\n<br />\n＾片中頭兩個變化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於發力，就要挺胸沈肩，想像用背肌發力<br />\n<br />\n(其實唔太get好正常，發力個人覺得唔洗急，我初初都完全唔知自己做緊乜，都係後尾拉得多熟左個動作，上網睇下教學，先至get 到)<br />\n<br />\n所以係只要係唔受傷既前題下，練多d拉多d，日子有功，就會明引體到底係如何發力"},{"pid":"a81b9ea44d24f3126f083b06f97227077862fc11","tid":840940,"uid":66740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"做到十一二下，但覺得用撚錯晒力，淨係用前臂力拉上去（正手），再錯係淨用右手...搞到成身左右極唔平衡，點修正"},{"pid":"e777ccf897a4ae920046562b0baa3ee5d5b0f552","tid":840940,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:04:54.000Z","msg":"其實都講得唔錯<br />\n可以參考下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccd0d3ce694b47aaf290759069513144784ead7","tid":840940,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"點樣防止下身搖擺"},{"pid":"a74e3cd761b2e19f1d7cab13fa6a6b14a1438f74","tid":840940,"uid":79943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:28:16.000Z","msg":"請問直手下拉對腹部嘅力量係咪需求好大，我完全發唔到力上去"},{"pid":"0a573d7994543b775622d22cc82ef47e2774b7e0","tid":840940,"uid":138477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以教我Muscle up"},{"pid":"acc6dcb10073446d857db2c3695ebe034b68d152","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a81b9ea44d24f3126f083b06f97227077862fc11","tid":840940,"uid":66740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"做到十一二下，但覺得用撚錯晒力，淨係用前臂力拉上去（正手），再錯係淨用右手...搞到成身左右極唔平衡，點修正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"我估係因為巴打冇沉肩夾背咁拉，所以變相用二頭前臂多（巴打拉上去既軌跡應該係接近c字，而想正確咁engage 到背肌既話，拉上去既軌跡其實係要直線）<br />\n<br />\n巴打拉果時盡量先*捱*後挺胸，然後先再拉，同時留意前臂係會lock死，手肘向自己臂部方向下拉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於 左右唔平衡要靠自己tune<br />\n<br />\n拎個cam影住自己，盡量左右平衡發力<br />\n<br />\n回頭睇番個form，覺得唔正宗就再執<br />\n<br />\n每次練次前都執執先練，好快有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9e1917e83db21b665ee15d1e0e64caa9945e89","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e777ccf897a4ae920046562b0baa3ee5d5b0f552","tid":840940,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:04:54.000Z","msg":"其實都講得唔錯<br />\n可以參考下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3b8c420a0d2a5b595bb054b152428a6dc9e7b6","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ccd0d3ce694b47aaf290759069513144784ead7","tid":840940,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"點樣防止下身搖擺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"做既時候記緊微微用力鎖緊腹部、臂部同大腿<br />\n<br />\n同埋避免好心急咁跳上去捉住支bar（好易會Fing 黎Fing 去，呢個時候砸拉引體自然會好唔穩定）<br />\n<br />\n慢慢黎腿實地捉住支bar/睇定d輕輕地，咁上到去個人就會定好多"},{"pid":"3ea9a061e113cd0670036bd9df1dbbb5ea6048d2","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a74e3cd761b2e19f1d7cab13fa6a6b14a1438f74","tid":840940,"uid":79943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:28:16.000Z","msg":"請問直手下拉對腹部嘅力量係咪需求好大，我完全發唔到力上去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"係，絕對會食到core <br />\n<br />\n但一般黎講最依既係背闊肌<br />\n<br />\n其實動作有一定難度，建議有10下 up以上引體先開始練"},{"pid":"8ba68f4a2d5e69ca10996fc18dada0b17dc939b8","tid":840940,"uid":116518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"拉到1 下。 點樣提升至7 8 下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0817de1bfe02ef1fb7ee419ba3d57660df8dbc22","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a573d7994543b775622d22cc82ef47e2774b7e0","tid":840940,"uid":138477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以教我Muscle up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:13:37.000Z","msg":"首先巴打基本功要合格<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得最低要求都要12 up引體 &amp; 15下dip <br />\n<br />\n然就開以做specially 真係for muscle up 既鍛練<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，就係要練explosive pull up 同straight bar dip (因為將muscle ups break down既話，就係exactly 呢兩個動作)<br />\n<br />\n建議將呢兩個動作放入workout既入面 (最理想係開頭)<br />\n<br />\n例如: explosive pull up 3~5 x 5 (注意，練爆炸力下數可以少，避免力竭)<br />\nStraight bar dip 6~10 x 5 <br />\n<br />\n^然後再做埋當日餘下既sets <br />\n<br />\n另外，有拉力帶既話，都可以試下做assisted muscle up<br />\n<br />\n體驗下壓胸、轉手腕、借助momentum既感覺"},{"pid":"9921a78f01207a541071f1271ef05f33e55019cc","tid":840940,"uid":19188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:18:46.000Z","msg":"粉嶺jj?"},{"pid":"2532826f13c015ad6dd21ef3a3cc3461ae072c3a","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba68f4a2d5e69ca10996fc18dada0b17dc939b8","tid":840940,"uid":116518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"拉到1 下。 點樣提升至7 8 下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:27:27.000Z","msg":"其實我會建議先練易d既引體變化，離心收縮引體/斜拉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理由就係：當你標準引體只能做得一下，而你又拎佢黎做訓練動作既話，個volume就會好少（好簡單既例子，當你拉五組正宗引體，其實五組落黎你都只係拉到五下）對力量適應同肌肉成長都十分不利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以就寧願做d簡單d既變化<br />\n<br />\n例如 斜拉，每組理應你會有能力做到6～12下<br />\n         離心收縮引體，應該都會做到3～5下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n具體黎講，可以先做幾組離心收縮，到冇乜力，再轉斜拉（組間大概抖2～3分鐘）<br />\n<br />\n一星期練番2～3次，引體數目好快上升<br />\n<br />\n到你拉到4～5下，就可以將正式將引體放入working set"},{"pid":"1223c7fe149cfc6adac6c6ad222d879fa0ac6993","tid":840940,"uid":54636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9921a78f01207a541071f1271ef05f33e55019cc","tid":840940,"uid":19188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:18:46.000Z","msg":"粉嶺jj?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:27:33.000Z","msg":"係，百福/雍盛苑"}]}